Electron version : 1.3.1
OS :Windows/MAC

Hi, 

I am trying to use "Alt+E" shortcut to open the Edit menu(similarly View & Help menu too) in my app. But it's not working. It doesn't open the menu. However, I've other accelerators in the sub menu which seems to be working fine. Below is the menu template. Can you tell me if this is an issue or I am not using it correctly ?


menuTemplate.push({
        label: "Edit",
        accelerator: "Alt+E",
        submenu: [
            {
                label: "Copy",
                accelerator: "CmdOrCtrl+C",
                role: "copy"
            },
            {
                label: "Cut",
                accelerator: "CmdOrCtrl+X",
                role: "cut"
            },
            {
                label: "Paste",
                accelerator: "CmdOrCtrl+V",
                role: "paste"
            }
        ]
    });


Thank you
